<section>
<section id="slide-org2963923">
<h2 id="org2963923">Expected Outcome</h2>
<ul>
<li>Provide a simple introduction to using flashcards,  active recall &amp; spaced repititon for learning</li>
<li>Eliminate the need to constantly read or make notes on the same topics</li>
<li>Help make studying a daily habit</li>

</ul>
</section>
